Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Bernstein.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Bernstein (1989), 41 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. D.D. 88-27 Submitted January 11, 1989 Decided February 8, 1989.)

Jan Michael Bernstein is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
